snippet.title: TOUR DE FRANCE 2025- ÉNORME CHUTE dans le final et sprint sous le DÉLUGE à Valence pour l'étape 17 !
snippet.description:
Jonathan Milan en a profité. Sur une 17e étape taillée pour les sprinteurs mercredi, l’Italien de la Lidl-Trek s’est imposé à Valence, au terme d’un sprint en comité réduit après une chute survenue dans le dernier kilomètre. Il en a profité pour prendre ses distances dans la course au maillot vert sur Tadej Pogacar, qui conserve la tunique jaune de leader au classement général.

Abonnez-vous pour ne rien manquer et visionner les résumés chaque jour seulement quelques minutes après l’arrivée de l’étape 👉 https://bit.ly/3OetlmT
------------------------------------------------------------
🇫🇷🚴 LE TOUR DE FRANCE 2025 💥

Trois semaines de course, des cols mythiques, des sprints à couper le souffle et des rebondissements à chaque virage : le Tour de France 2025 est lancé !Suivez l’élite du cyclisme mondial sur les routes les plus exigeantes de l’Hexagone. Des pavés du Nord aux sommets alpins, chaque étape est un moment de vérité. Qui portera le maillot jaune à Paris ? Qui fera exploser le peloton ?

🔥 Les grands favoris de cette édition
* 🟡 Tadej Pogačar (UAE Emirates)
* 🔵 Jonas Vingegaard (Visma–Lease a Bike)
* 🔴 Remco Evenepoel (Soudal–Quick Step)
* 🟢 Primož Roglič (Red Bull - BORA hansgrohe)
* ⚫ Carlos Rodríguez (INEOS Grenadiers)
Et vous, sur qui misez-vous cette année ? 💬

snippet.title: AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH - Trailer (2025) James Cameron | 20th century studios
snippet.description:
#avatar #jamescameron #disney 

— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

—  In this concept trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash, Jake Sully and his family stand at the center of a brewing war that threatens to consume Pandora in flame and ash. Years after uniting the clans of water and sky, Jake must now confront a new Na’vi enemy — the Ash People, led by the ruthless Varang, whose power to wield fire and reject the old ways fractures Pandora’s fragile balance. As ancient beliefs clash and old wounds reopen, Spider’s loyalty is tested, humans return with hidden motives, and the Sully family faces betrayal from within. With volcanoes stirring and sacred lands under siege, the clans must unite once more — water against fire, hope against hate — to protect their home from burning to nothing but ashes.
 
—  Subscribe to Teaser Universe 🎬
—  For inquiries: teaseruniverse@gmail.com 📩

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
First hunt. Last chance.

From the director of Prey, watch the brand-new trailer for Predator: Badlands, in theaters November 7.

“Predator: Badlands,” which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator, outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

snippet.title: Stavo - Climat (clip officiel)

"Climat”, c’est le monde vu par Stavo : instable, dangereux, mais toujours maîtrisé.
